However, I'm still wondering why this is all necessary as your examples, e.g. gitHubEvents also contain nested fields "foo.bar" and there no special transformation configuration is needed. The only difference I see is, I'm using AVRO where the gitHubEvents example uses JSON.

Maybe you wanna have a look at this as well, but I guess this ticket can be closed. Thanks to all for supporting me here, I'll continue my test with Pinot.

